lead_paragraph: So all these years later, it sure sounds as if Stephen Strasburg signed a $175 million, seven-year contract with the Washington Nationals precisely because of their decision to end his 2012 season before the playoffs — not despite it.

headline.print_headline: Strasburg's 2012 Shutdown Helped Lead to $175M, 7-Year Deal
headline.main: Strasburg's 2012 Shutdown Helped Lead to $175M, 7-Year Deal
